"""
Synthetic event harness for InfiniBot.

Fires fabricated Discord events directly through the bot's real event handlers (no gateway
connection) to measure hot-path throughput and event-loop lag.

Usage:
    python3 ./src/event_harness.py [options]

See documentation/event_harness.md for full usage details.
"""

